message.content: cs.IR, cs.DL, cs.DB, cs.CY, cs.HC. The paper discusses extending test collections for information retrieval (IR) purposes by incorporating external resources, specifically using OXPath to harvest data from web resources. This aligns with the sub-categories of Information Retrieval (cs.IR), Digital Libraries (cs.DL), and Databases (cs.DB). Additionally, the paper mentions the potential use of the extended collection for bibliometrics-enhanced retrieval, which falls under the sub-category of Cybernetics (cs.CY). Finally, the paper discusses the social sciences portal Sowiport, which could be relevant to the sub-category of Human-Computer Interaction (cs.HC).
